<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#AddCommMonoid\">AddCommMonoid</a> <span class=\"fn\">P</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Module/Defs.html#Module\">Module</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span> <span class=\"fn\">M</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Module/Defs.html#Module\">Module</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span> <span class=\"fn\">N</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\">M</span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Hom/Defs.html#AddMonoidHom\">→+</a> <span class=\"fn\">N</span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Hom/Defs.html#AddMonoidHom\">→+</a> <span class=\"fn\">P</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hf</span> : <span class=\"fn\">∀ (<span class=\"fn\">r</span> : <span class=\"fn\">R</span>) (<span class=\"fn\">m</span> : <span class=\"fn\">M</span>) (<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <span class=\"fn\">N</span>), <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> (<span class=\"fn\">r</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HSMul.hSMul\">•</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span>))</span> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\">m</span>)</span> (<span class=\"fn\">r</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HSMul.hSMul\">•</a> <span class=\"fn\">n</span>)</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/TensorProduct/Defs.html#TensorProduct\">TensorProduct</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span> <span class=\"fn\">M</span> <span class=\"fn\">N</span></span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Hom/Defs.html#AddMonoidHom\">→+</a> <span class=\"fn\">P</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Lift an `R`-balanced map to the tensor product.\nA map `f : M →+ N →+ P` additive in both components is `R`-balanced, or middle linear with respect\nto `R`, if scalar multiplication in either argument is equivalent, `f (r • m) n = f m (r • n)`.\nNote that strictly the first action should be a right-action by `R`, but for now `R` is commutative\nso it doesn't matter. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/TensorProduct/Basic.html#TensorProduct.liftAddHom","kind":"def","line":51,"name":"TensorProduct.liftAddHom","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/8f9d9cff6bd728b17a24e163c9402775d9e6a365/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/TensorProduct/Basic.lean#L51-L77"}}],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.LinearAlgebra.TensorProduct.Defs"],"instances":[{"className":"Neg","name":"TensorProduct.neg","typeNames":["TensorProduct"]},{"className":"AddCommGroup","name":"TensorProduct.addCommGroup","typeNames":["TensorProduct"]},{"className":"TensorProduct.CompatibleSMul","name":"TensorProduct.CompatibleSMul.int","typeNames":["Int"]},{"className":"TensorProduct.CompatibleSMul","name":"TensorProduct.CompatibleSMul.unit","typeNames":["Units"]}],"name":"Mathlib.LinearAlgebra.TensorProduct.Basic"}